Step 1 - Download this repository or clone it.
Step 2 - Go to takehome-frontend folder in your terminal, then type "npm install" to install all dependencies.
Step 3 - Then run "npm run dev" to start the application.
Step 4 - Now navigate to the takehome-backend folder in your termianal.
Step 5 - Run "node server.js" to start the server.